            "answer_text": "Human civilization is more likely to advance when the population is well-educated and has a firm stock of knowledge to build on. An ignorant population ends up doing menial labor to benefit more advanced foreign nations. Liberals are very much in favor of education. Human civilization is more likely to advance when they are continually trying new methods and ideas and adopting the ones that work. Conservatives try to protect traditional methods and ideology, even when they don\u2019t work. Liberals are skeptical of tradition and in favor of change. Human civilization is more likely to advance when civilization is stable and the population is invested in the societal structure. If people are starving, they lose that societal investment and turn to crime to feed themeselves and their families. If a lot of people are starving, nations become vulnerable. Look at what happened in Russia, France, and Cuba. Look at what nearly happened in Ireland. Liberals want to protect the stability of civilization by keeping the poorest people from becoming desperate and dangerous. Human civilization is more likely to advance when it is healthy. Pandemic health crises can decimate the population and destroy the economy. But if a person in generally good health catches a terrible disease, he has a fighting chance of surviving and getting better. If a person in poor health catches a terrible disease, it is almost certainly going to kill him. A healthy population is a resilient population. It will fare better if a new disease sweeps through the nation. Liberals are in favor of high-quality healthcare for all people. Human civilization is more likely to advance when all members of the society are able to contribute to the best of their ability. When women are prevented from advancing in their careers despite ability and hard work, society suffers. When a high-performing person is not permitted to perform at the highest level of their ability, then all they would have accomplished is lost to us. When minorities are kept in menial jobs, locked in poverty, and deprived of opportunity, everything they would have accomplished is lost to us. When those accomplishments do not happen, human civilization advances more slowly than it would have otherwise. Liberals are greatly in favor of ending sexism and racism. Liberals are in favor of education, ingenuity, stable society, a healthy population, and opportunity for advancement for everybody. All these things advance civilization. The real question is, why do conservatives oppose them? ",
